OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FNorthern and
OL,6,Feastern Scotland, the north of
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland, along with eastern
OL,8,Fparts of England will see areas of
OL,9,Fcloud and patchy rain overnight. Dry
OL,10,Felsewhere with clear spells and some
OL,11,Fmist or fog patches. Rather warm in
OL,12,Fmost areas.
OL,13,
OL,14,CThursday:FNorthwest Scotland could see
OL,15,Fsome rain tomorrow, and isolated
OL,16,Fshowers are possible across the far
OL,17,Feast and southeast of England. Fine
OL,18,Felsewhere with some very warm spells
OL,19,Fof sunshine.
